{
  "stem": "7684.1",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's the first time that they took some Dutch people out of the trail-- train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he'd say to all of us, go on the side.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was our luck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were all young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they all told us, go on the side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we had no idea what they want with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we saw all the women and children walking-- right.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they went to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the men were sitting on the side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had to take their shoes off and had to band them with the shoelaces together.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because, later on, I know that everything was sent to Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So when the shoelace is not together, then they get the shoe separated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I heard a German speaking to them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody got a little card.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the German spoke to them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're here in Sobibor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we will take care of you, and-- and write to home that you came safe here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Dutch people did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Dutch people didn't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- when they passed the Germans, they took their hat off when they had a hat on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody-- the Dutch transport didn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't know anything what-- what was going on-- definitely none-- none from the Dutch people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They just walked to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I remember one day, I see so for me that it was-- they said to the-- that you're going to take a shower.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they had took all the clothes already off-- when they had to put it together on the-- there with the banded shoes.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they run.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they say, come, come, come, we take a shower!",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "To-- they're screaming to each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
